article.description: — Marcus Domask had 14 points as Southern Illinois rolled past Southern Miss 66-41 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Domask lifts S. Illinois past Southern Miss 66-41
article.linkText: Domask lifts S. Illinois past Southern Miss 66-41
article.story: CARBONDALE, Ill. -- — Marcus Domask had 14 points as Southern Illinois rolled past Southern Miss 66-41 on Saturday night. Lance Jones had 11 points for Southern Illinois (5-3). Ben Coupet Jr. added 11 points. Steven Verplancken Jr. had 10 points. Walyn Napper had 15 points for the Golden Eagles (4-5). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
